12:11.000 --> 12:16.000
Secondly, it is enough to part with him painlessly.

12:16.000 --> 12:24.000
That is why specialization in these companies balances at the level of the threshold of specialization.

12:24.000 --> 12:37.000
Because people who come to this company must quickly master the skills necessary for the operation and pass these skills on to another person who will come to this company in two or three months.

12:38.000 --> 12:53.000
Other companies, for example, consulting business, which are interested in minimizing brain drain in other companies, competitors and, perhaps, even in other states, will build different strategies.

12:53.000 --> 12:59.000
And in such companies, very often, specialization is quite broad.

12:59.000 --> 13:04.000
