And you know very well that, let's say, in a functional structure or a divisional structure, there are departments in a company that, firstly, unite people with certain skills and knowledge, and, secondly, perform certain functions in the organization.

13:41.000 --> 13:49.000
Thirdly, the main factor of influence on how we design work is, of course, our main business processes.

13:49.000 --> 14:00.000
