14:08.000 --> 14:21.000
These are completely different businesses, different business processes, and the business processes themselves will affect how we design the work of our subordinates.

14:22.000 --> 14:31.000
And, of course, probably the most important factor is the internal motives of each employee for whom we design this work.

14:31.000 --> 14:38.000
In some cases, we can say, no, we have a company called Uravnilovka, we all have official instructions.

