16:44.000 --> 16:54.000
So, we simply cannot perform work in an organization alone. In order to do it, we need to interact.

16:54.000 --> 17:11.000
Interact at the same hierarchy level where we are, interact with the management, and all these interactions will be supported by certain rules and norms of behavior fixed in the corporate culture of our company.

17:11.000 --> 17:14.000
Therefore, this is also very important.

17:14.000 --> 17:23.000
