18:31.000 --> 18:56.000
He himself was involved in the control measures to assess the quality of the performance of this work, his timeliness, and so on, and had the opportunity and the inner desire to change something so that the work could be performed better, more effectively, and, in some cases, even easier, and, of course, more interesting for him.

