57:10.000 --> 57:34.000
Just like the software we buy sets certain requirements for the computer we try to install, the social system also sets certain requirements for our information technologies that are introduced into the corporate life of a modern company.

57:34.000 --> 57:49.000
This difference between the requirements set by the social system of the organization and the opportunities provided by modern automation means is called a socio-technical gap.

