because the company supplied expensive equipment, and any agreement or will to sign a contract, to change a contract, had to be resolved incredibly quickly.

59:28.000 --> 59:36.000
Sales managers thought that these issues could be solved quickly only by direct contact.

59:36.000 --> 59:49.000
Over time, this situation was resolved, managers were trained, they got used to this system, set certain requirements for the system, which had to be finalized by the programmers.

59:49.000 --> 59:56.000
Only then did it work in the organization. This happens very often.

